law.text:
This Part VII of this subtitle (Two and One-Half/One Percent Compound Adjustment) applies to an allowance based on creditable service earned on or after July 1, 2011, for:
a former member, retiree, or surviving spouse of a member of:
the Correctional Officers' Retirement System;
the Employees' Pension System;
the Law Enforcement Officers' Pension System;
the State Police Retirement System; or
the Teachers' Pension System; or
a beneficiary of the retiree or former member described in item (1) of this section.
